Package: r2zotero
Type: Package
Title: Send suggested citations from R directly to Zotero
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ethan", "Bass", , "ethanbass@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6175-6739"))
  )
Maintainer: Ethan Bass <ethanbass@gmail.com>
Description: Uses the Zotero JSON web API to send citations from the 'CITATION'
    file directly to a local Zotero library.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ethanbass/r2zotero/
BugReports: https://github.com/ethanbass/r2zotero/issues/
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
